Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.62,TITLE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fr89\fs45\pos(705,544)\c&H0B0059&}公共电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优子 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗 火村前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起离开这个城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我连一秒都不想再让你呆在那种地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是自作主张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起去没有那家伙的地方重新生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能随我一起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真霸道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.35,0:00:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 既然你都这么说了

Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:56.10,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Love, I've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:59.34,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}If you put your trust in me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.75,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I know what my life would be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:07.96,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Oh, you are all I ever need
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:13.63,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I try to hear what you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:15.79,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}So I pray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:19.38,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}But you're fading away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:26.55,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Don't go and break my fragile heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:30.08,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}We won't fall apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:38.15,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}'Cause you're my only star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.96,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I wonder why my tears come at night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.40,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Calling you, so like a little child
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:50.67,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}All the things you have in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.08,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}I wish I could say your insides
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.09,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}My love, you've got to feel it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:02:00.62,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}And if we put our trust in you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:04.20,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}You know what our lives would be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:11.51,OPEN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,15)\fad(300,300)}Oh, you are the one I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:59.34,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}落花有意 流水无情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:07.96,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}茅塞顿开 一见倾心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:15.79,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}逾墙钻隙 默默祈冀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:19.38,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}然却汝身 若即若离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:26.55,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}天涯海角 绵绵无期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:38.15,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}海誓山盟 专心如一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:43.96,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}谁与剪烛 兀自饮泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:47.40,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}垂髫总角 呼唤不息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:54.08,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}肝胆相照 心有灵犀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:57.09,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}吾依吾爱 二情依依
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:02:04.20,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}若相见信 生死不离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.90,0:02:11.51,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,1065)\fad(300,300)}笙磬同音 我心永寄
